Is there any chance
you could just untie me and let me go?

01:21:02.756 --> 01:21:06.317
Oh. no. It would set a bad precedent.

01:21:06.627 --> 01:21:07.651
RATHGAR:
Fine.

01:21:07.828 --> 01:21:09.819
Did I mention
that I am Rathgal the Wizard?

01:21:09.997 --> 01:21:11.226
Not to boast.

01:21:11.398 --> 01:21:14.368
Ah. My brothel used to have
a helmet like that.

01:21:14.535 --> 01:21:16.765
Perhaps you know him? Eric the Large?

01:21:16.937 --> 01:21:18.928
A Viking? A large man?

01:21:19.106 --> 01:21:22.167
A large Viking man?
Ah. yes. yes. I know him.

01:21:22.776 --> 01:21:24.904
[ALL YELL]

