01:21:44.765 --> 01:21:49.532
Prepare to grovel for mercy.

01:21:49.703 --> 01:21:51.603
[GNOMES CHATTERING
AND MAKING KISSING NOISES]

01:21:51.772 --> 01:21:53.467
Ew.

01:21:54.174 --> 01:21:56.939
You're disgusting. I feel unclean.

01:21:57.111 --> 01:21:59.307
- Then you'll let us go?
- No.

01:21:59.480 --> 01:22:01.312
GNOMES [WHIMPERING]:
Please. please.

01:22:01.482 --> 01:22:02.711
Silence.

01:22:02.883 --> 01:22:05.250
[ALL CRYING]

01:22:05.419 --> 01:22:07.353
I said. silence. you horrid gnomes.

01:22:07.821 --> 01:22:10.483
Prepare to receive
a horrible. twisting curse...

01:22:10.657 --> 01:22:12.182
...that will last 4000 years.

01:22:12.359 --> 01:22:14.521
I've got a full day ahead, so let's go.

01:22:16.029 --> 01:22:19.693
- I'm going to apologize.
