01:22:22.636 --> 01:22:24.297
Hold your curse, Hathgal.

01:22:25.038 --> 01:22:26.802
Mugging you and your brothel
was wrong.

01:22:26.974 --> 01:22:30.774
For my deeds. I wish to say I'm--

01:22:30.944 --> 01:22:33.936
[BABBLING INDISTINCTLY]

01:22:36.416 --> 01:22:37.508
--Sony.

01:22:37.684 --> 01:22:38.810
[COUGHING AND SPITTING]

01:22:39.820 --> 01:22:42.949
My goodness.
A gnome actually apologized.

01:22:43.123 --> 01:22:44.852
And the rest of you?

01:22:45.025 --> 01:22:46.993
[GNOMES MURMURING]

01:22:47.161 --> 01:22:49.255
Your willingness to change
has so impressed me...

01:22:49.429 --> 01:22:51.693
...that I will effect a different curse.

01:22:51.865 --> 01:22:55.768
Can you make slow, overweight birds
appear out of thin air?

01:22:55.936 --> 01:22:58.405
Yes. but I won't.

01:22:58.572 --> 01:23:00.404
Since you used the day for mischief...

01:23:00.574 --> 01:23:03.339
...henceforth the sunlight
will transform you into statues.

01:23:03.510 --> 01:23:05.706
Only during the night will you know life.

01:23:05.879 --> 01:23:08.211
You will live like this
until you mend your ways...

01:23:08.382 --> 01:23:10.783
...and serve mankind
without profit or gain.

01:23:10.951 --> 01:23:13.716
The sooner you change.
the sooner the curse is over.

01:23:13.887 --> 01:23:16.788
So there. you're cursed. Goodbye.

01:23:20.060 --> 01:23:21.221
That's not so bad.

01:23:21.395 --> 01:23:23.796
We'll have this curse beat
in a couple of weeks.

01:23:23.964 --> 01:23:25.227
Piece of cake .

01:23:31.605 --> 01:23:34.575
<i>BAFFEARMN:
